room_title: Escape room "Taken" by Deadbolt - Boneyfiddle Escape Rooms and Mysteries in Portsmouth (OH)
room_description: You are invited to an interview with acclaimed surgeon Dr. Susan Carrington. This could be your big break for your career! As you sit alone in the conference room, you notice a strong odor... everything goes black. You awake in a haze, and notice you are chained and blindfolded, along with others. In walks a woman in a lab coat and surgical mask... she laughs and then walks out. Will you escape before you find out what she has in store?
